data.description: This 2021 built home boasting 1,500+ square feet was constructed by Ryan Homes in the newly sought-after subdivision of Cypress Preserve in Land O’ Lakes. Don''t wait months for a new build home when you can have this one right away and still under the builder's warranty. All bedrooms and great room consist of modern ceiling fans. When you approach the kitchen, you will see the large island with beautiful countertops and a walk-in pantry. You will find dual sinks in the primary bathroom, and a separate door leading into a walk-in closet! As you walk out of the sliding glass doors you’ll be greeted with an oversized rear yard with a recently installed partial vinyl fence! Cypress Preserve offers its residents many amenities, including multiple dog parks, a large and vibrant pool area, and a large playground with incredibly low HOA fees and affordable CDD fees. Take a stroll through this amenity-rich community to take advantage of all it has to offer. Cypress Preserve includes a resort-style zero-entry pool, dog park, playground, large event lawn, and walking trails.
